title: Eric Swalwell announces run for California governor, vows to be 'protector and fighter'
text: Rep. Eric Swalwell, D-Calif., announced on Thursday he is launching a campaign for California governor in 2026.
summary: Rep. Eric Swalwell, D-Calif., announced on Thursday he is launching a campaign for California governor in 2026.
